                <div class="text-7xl font-black text-[#F5521A] leading-none tracking-tight">8.8</div>
                <div class="text-xs text-gray-600 uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-black mt-2">OUT OF 10</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-4 font-medium border-t border-gray-200 pt-4">
                  Only real e-commerce option
